22:
I thought my outfit felt a little tight
today—when I went to weigh myself,
I...
26:
I discovered that...
I gained a whole FIVE pounds!
32:
Well... We all could stand to watch
our waistlines after the holiday
festivities.
37:
It just doesn't make any sense! I
mean, I didn't even eat that much!
42:
Didn't you JUST win an eating
contest recently?
47:
That wasn't even me though! It was
the shadows' doing!
52:
Hmm... Where does all that food go
anyway?
61:
I see. It makes sense you would
absorb any energy consumed by
your shadows.
66:
So you're saying it's THEIR fault I can
barely fit into my clothes lately?!
70:
I-I suppose that's one way of putting
it.
75:
And not only that, I didn't even get to
taste any of it...
79: Shadows, come out here this instant!
90:
So NOW you wanna hide, huh? Is
that how it is?!
100:
H-hey! I'm sure you'll be back to
your old self in no time.
106: You just don't get it, do you, Nimbus?
108:
Why is it that if my SHADOWS do
something, I'M the one who has to
deal with the consequences!
112:
It's not fair! I shouldn't be punished
for THEIR behavior!
117:
I have an idea, actually. Have you
heard of seven-herb porridge?
122:
Is that some kind of miracle food
that'll change me back to normal?
125:
Not exactly, but I hear it does a body
good if you've had a bit too much to
eat.
130:
That sounds perfect! Let's make
some right away!
133:
The herbs can only be found in
Yamato... Did you want to go look for
them?
144:
Sheesh, all this fuss over a few
pounds. Well, good luck out there.
147:
What are you saying, Nimbus?
You're coming too!
154:
The more help we can get, the faster
we'll be done!
159:
I've never seen Rebecca look this
serious about anything before.
163:
Careful, guys. There have been
reports of monsters in this area, so—
173:
Okay! That should be everything. Alk,
do your magic!
186:
Phew... I ended up eating quite a bit
myself.
190:
Appreciate you mixing it up with the
meatballs for mine, Alk. Meat makes
everything better!
194:
I was quite fond of the tomato
risotto arrangement for mine as well.
202:
But I just have to bear with it for
now! And then I can treat myself
later to one with... melted... cheese...
214:
N-nothing, it's just... I thought I still
had some left over.
221:
Uh-oh. Those shadows of yours, uh,
really have an appetite, huh?
226: You have GOT to be kidding me!
230: Grr... I am SO done with this!
234:
Come out here and answer for your
crimes already!
